name: Giclee Canvas print " Angel" (84 x 58cm)
description:
Signed Giclee print on canvas with stretcher (84 x 58 cm)
by published illustrator Al Gray . 

Al Gray has worked as a Freelance illustrator for the last fourteen years. Clients include; Guinness, GQ (USA), Esquire, The Independent and The Telegraph newspaper to name but a few.
